<HEADLINE> S. African Parliament Speaker Elected to </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESUBRG, January 20 (Xinhua) -- Frene Ginwala, Speaker of
the South African National Assembly, was elected to fill Africa's
seat on the Standing Committee of the Conference of Commonwealth
at its recent meeting in Trinidad and Tobago, Ginwala's office
said in a statement today.
</P>
