<HEADLINE> France Dedicates Round Stamp to Football World Cup </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, January 20 (Xinhua) -- A round stamp representing the
figure of a football was unveiled Tuesday by French post officials
to mark the 1998 Football World Cup finals to be held this Summer
in France.
</P>
<P>
The stamp, with the value of three francs, represents the
figure of a blue football and has the logo France 98 on it against
a background of flags.
</P>
<P>
The stamp will be sold in the 10 French cities where the
matches will be held, said post officials. 
</P>
