Aziz and Butler held the first session of talks Monday evening
and are due to hold a third one Tuesday evening.
</P>
<P>
Xinhua correspondent learned that Butler, who arrived here
Monday, had met ambassadors of the five permanent member states of
the U.N. Security Council here to brief them on the main points in
his talks with the Iraqi side, and that Butler would also meet a
number of other foreign diplomats Wednesday morning. 
