contracted value of 31 million U.S. dollars, or 41 percent of
total investments.
</P>
<P>
Liaoning's attainment of grain self-sufficiency represents
marked progress for province which was a heavy industrial base for
many decades. The ongoing industrialization of agriculture
indicates a second major leap in agricultural production,
according to the official. 
</P>
