East peace process in his meeting with Palestinian leader Yasir
Arafat on Thursday.
</P>
<P>
There is a series of issues to be addressed before the
collapsed peace process could be pulled back on track, which
include "further redeployment, security steps by the Palestinians
and what the Israelis required, what would be the timetable," the
official said. 
