<HEADLINE> Australian Dollar Closes Unchanged </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CANBERRA, January 21 (Xinhua) -- The Australian dollar failed
at its third attempt to break 67 US cents Wednesday, as the
continuing financial crisis in Asia eroded offshore gains.
</P>
<P>
The Australian dollar closed unchanged at 66.23 US cents, but
well off its opening highs of 66.78 US cents.
</P>
<P>
