<HEADLINE> Xinhua Stock Indexes Changed Mixedly </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, January 21 (Xinhua) -- Today's Xinhua A stock index
lost 1.00 point to close at 154.13, while the Xinhua B stock
index lost 0.97 point to finish at 45.67.
</P>
<P>
The Xinhua Stock index is China's first national unitary stock
exponent, which is jointly designed and issued by the Economic
Information Department of the Xinhua News Agency and Beijing
University.  
