two countries' friendly cooperation, according to Chinese
diplomats close to the meeting.
</P>
<P>
On his part, Maciel spoke highly about the full-fledged growth
of bilateral relations in various fields since the two countries
established diplomatic ties 20 years ago.
</P>
<P>
The Exchange of visits by senior officials have further
propelled the expansion of Sino-Brazilian cooperation, he noted.
</P>
