of Thai frozen chicken as competitive as those from low-cost
producers like China and Brazil.
</P>
<P>
"The prospects of Thai Frozen chicken exports look especially
bright this year," Suthep said.
</P>
<P>
The bird flu scare may help increase Thai frozen chicken
exports to Hong Kong although it is unlikely to jump significantly
given Hong Kong's preference for fresh chicken, he said.  
